					"patching_rect" : [ 470.0, 301.0, 267.0, 114.0 ],
					"text" : "Inlet 1: value x in range [0,1] => [0,1] to map\nInlet 2: sigmoid or logit steepness parameter a\n - a>0: sigmoid_ab(x)\n - a<0: logit_ab(x)\n - a=0: x\nInlet 3: sigmoid or logit shift parameter b [0,1]\n - a>0: shift along x-axis\n - a<0: shift along y-axis",
